Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:45.02,ZHU,,0,0,0,,一九六九年三月三日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:48.03,ZHU,,0,0,0,,美國海軍為戰機師 成立了一間精英學校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:51.03,ZHU,,0,0,0,,目的是教導機師快將失傳的空戰技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:54.03,ZHU,,0,0,0,,以確保在此畢業的一小撮機師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:55.83,ZHU,,0,0,0,,成為世上最一流的戰機師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:57.03,ZHU,,0,0,0,,他們成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:00:59.04,ZHU,,0,0,0,,現在 海軍稱之為戰鬥學校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:01.13,ZHU,,0,0,0,,戰機師則稱之為頂級機師部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:06.11,ZHU,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,2000)\fs150\fscx130\fsp10}壯志淩雲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:11.10,ZHU,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}印度洋 現代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 史葛 早  - 溫斯 早\N{\rENG}- Morning, Scott  - Morning, Vince
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 威斯 早  - 長官 早\N{\rENG}- Morning, Wells  - Morning, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:17.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你好嗎\N{\rENG}Okey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,騎鬼者 這兒是空襲部\N{\rENG}Ghost Rider, this is Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,發現不明戰機 回程的軍官\N{\rENG}We have unknown aircraft Inbound, Mustang
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,循〇九〇方飛向敵機\N{\rENG}Your vector, 0-9-0 for bogey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:39.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,上面的是誰\N{\rENG}Who's up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅 灰背隼 馬華力和野鵝\N{\rENG}Cougar and Merlin and Maverick and Goose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:45.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,好極 是馬華力和野鵝\N{\rENG}Great Maverick and Goose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,野鵝 快回答\N{\rENG}Talk to me, Goose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:57.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,收到 我看到他了\N{\rENG}Roger, I got him.Contact, 20 left at 30 miles
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:01.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,在左面三十哩 以時速九百海海裡飛近\N{\rENG}Nine hundred knots closure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅 你聽到嗎\N{\rENG}Cougar, you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\rENG}Roger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 灰背隼 看到他嗎  - 收到 雷達探測到了\N{\rENG}- Merlin, you got him?  - Roger, I've got radar contact
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:09.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要親眼確定他 美洲獅 你去引他上釣\N{\rENG}I'll get a visual ID.Cougar, you hook him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,收到 我會將他煎皮拆骨\N{\rENG}Roger, and I'll clean him and fry him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,軍官 這是騎鬼者 我們在二〇三方\N{\rENG}Mustang, Mustang, this is Ghost Rider, 2-0-3,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:26.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,他受制於我了 他向二七〇方前進\N{\rENG}I've got him inbound, bogey heading 2-7-0,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:29.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,距離十哩 以九百海海裡前進\N{\rENG}We're at ten miles, 900 knots closure,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:32.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,騎鬼者 向上十度 向左三度 零\N{\rENG}Ghost Rider, take Angels ten left, 3-0
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:35.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我們今天應該有訪客嗎？  - 不\N{\rENG}- Are we supposed to have visitors today?  - Negative, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,灰背隼 看看他是不是一個人\N{\rENG}Merlin, see if he's a single
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:45.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\rENG}Roger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,野鵝 看到跟蹤者嗎\N{\rENG}Goose, you see a trailer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:50.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒有 灰背隼\N{\rENG}Negative, Merlin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,似乎只有他一個\N{\rENG}Looks like he's a single
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:54.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅 我要和他正面交鋒\N{\rENG}Cougar, I'm gonna go head-to-head with him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力 別亂來 我不同意\N{\rENG}Take it easy, Maverick I don't like this shit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,我飛高一些 確定是不是只有他一個\N{\rENG}I'm gonna break high and right,see if he's really alone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力 他以一千海海裡接近\N{\rENG}We've got 1000 knots closure, Mav
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:22.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,他向著我們飛過來\N{\rENG}He's coming right at us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,老友 你在想什麼\N{\rENG}Okay, buddy, what's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:28.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊 他們有兩個人\N{\rENG}Holy shit, there's two of them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,是米格28 沒人試過這麼近看到\N{\rENG}MiG-28s No one's been this close before
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:34.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們究竟在做什麼 什麼位置\N{\rENG}What the hell are they doing here?What's the position?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,距離二百五十哩\N{\rENG}Two hundred and fifty miles out, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:38.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,二百五十哩 叫他們馬上離開\N{\rENG}Two hundred and fifty miles? Get them out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:43.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅 你看到米格機一號 我去追二號\N{\rENG}Cougar, you've got MiG one.I'm going after MiG two
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:46.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,我在陽光下不見了他\N{\rENG}I lost him in the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:51.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,該死 他在做什麼 灰背隼 你制住他了嗎\N{\rENG}Shit What's he doing? You got him, Merlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:55.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,他在四處飛 他跟著我們飛\N{\rENG}He's coming around.He's coming around on our tail
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:59.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,該死 被他制住了\N{\rENG}Goddamn it This bogey's all over me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:05.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 現在距離多遠  - 二百哩\N{\rENG}- What's their range now?  - Two hundred miles, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,短過一百五十哩的話 就出動五號戒備機\N{\rENG}If they break 150 miles, launch the Alert Five aircraft
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:10.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,是 長官\N{\rENG}Yes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:13.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,空速三百 馬華力 消滅他\N{\rENG}Air speed, 300 Go get him, Mav
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我準備鎖定導彈\N{\rENG}I'm going for missile lock
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,看看能不能把他嚇走\N{\rENG}Let's see if we can scare this guy out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:23.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,快鎖定 親愛的\N{\rENG}Come on, lock up, baby.Lock up, baby Lock up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,鎖定吧 已經鎖定了\N{\rENG}I got him locked Bingo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,嚇倒他了 馬華力 他夾著尾巴逃走\N{\rENG}We got him, Mav He's bugging out and going home
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,軍官 我是馬華力 米格機二號回去了\N{\rENG}Mustang, this is Maverick MiG two is headed home
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:40.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 他們是什麼位置\N{\rENG}All right What's their position?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:43.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,距離一百八十哩 方位是〇一〇\N{\rENG}A hundred and eighty miles at bearing 0-1-0, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,他的導彈瞄準我們了 快點避開他\N{\rENG}Cougar, he's got missile lock on us.Get away from this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼一回事 他追著我\N{\rENG}What the hell is this shit? He's engaging me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:56.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,該死 軍官 這是騎鬼者一一七號\N{\rENG}Goddamn it, Mustang.This is Ghost Rider, 1-1-7
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我被敵機制住了 他用導彈鎖定我了\N{\rENG}This bogey's all over me He's got missile lock on me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:07:59.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我能得到開火的批准嗎\N{\rENG}Permission to fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:02.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,未受襲前不能開火\N{\rENG}Do not fire until fired upon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:06.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,野鵝 他們就在我們下面\N{\rENG}Goose, there they are, right below us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,米格機在最佳的開火位置 他在美洲獅後面\N{\rENG}The MiG's in perfect firing position.He's right on Cougar's tail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:10.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,不可能 野鵝\N{\rENG}No way, Goose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:12.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,他早就應該開火了 他只是想激怒我們\N{\rENG}He'd have fired by now He's just trying to piss us off
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:15.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力 快來幫我脫身\N{\rENG}Maverick, get down here and get this asshole off me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅 別緊張\N{\rENG}Easy, Cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:23.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,帶他回來 協助我進入戰場\N{\rENG}Bring it back, hard right Help me engage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我來了\N{\rENG}I'm on my way
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我無法射擊這個王八蛋\N{\rENG}I can't shoot this son of a bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,看看我們能不能跟他玩玩\N{\rENG}Let's see if we can have a little fun with him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:54.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,你說的“玩玩”就是這樣\N{\rENG}Is this your idea of fun, Mav?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rENG}Greetings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,小心戰機\N{\rENG}Watch the birdie
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊 笑死我了\N{\rENG}Jeez, I crack myself up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:17.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,這種景象很精彩 我應該當攝影師\N{\rENG}This is a great shot, Mav I should be a photographer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅\N{\rENG}Cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:20.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,你脫身了 米格機一號離開了\N{\rENG}your tail is clear MiG one's bugged out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅 我是馬華力\N{\rENG}Cougar, this is Maverick
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:36.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,今天玩得真開心呢 是嗎\N{\rENG}We've had enough fun for one day, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:40.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,燃料不多了 我們回去吧\N{\rENG}I'm getting a little low on fuel, so we're heading home
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,在甲板上見\N{\rENG}We'll see you on deck
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:56.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,飛洲獅 燃料不多 要走了\N{\rENG}Cougar, we're running low on gas,we gotta get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅\N{\rENG}Cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:06.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,快沒燃料了 美洲獅 快回去\N{\rENG}We're on vapor, Cougar Let's do it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:10.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅 快回去\N{\rENG}Cougar Come on, Cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:23.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,快飛回艦上 飛洲獅\N{\rENG}Let's take it back to the ship, man, Come on, Cougar,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:26.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,叫他儘快降落 他快沒燃料了\N{\rENG}Get him on deck as soon as possible.He's gotta be low on fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅 我們要降落\N{\rENG}Cougar, we gotta land this thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:33.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們快沒燃料了 你明白嗎\N{\rENG}We are way low on gas You understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧\N{\rENG}You all right, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:45.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力 還有四分三哩 降落時作出通知\N{\rENG}Maverick, you're at three-quarters of a mile, call the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,收到 馬華力快要降落\N{\rENG}Roger Maverick has the ball
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:50.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅 要降落了 快點回去\N{\rENG}Cougar, it is time to land, Let's do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:52.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,野鵝 美洲獅出了事\N{\rENG}Goose, Cougar's in trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:55.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,別亂來 我們快沒燃料了 快點降落\N{\rENG}Come on, Mav, we're getting low on gas.Let's land this sucker
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:58.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅\N{\rENG}Cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,該死 馬華力\N{\rENG}Goddamn it, Maverick
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:09.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼 我們不夠燃料這樣做\N{\rENG}What are you doing, Mav?we've got no fuel for this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:10.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們要去幫美洲獅\N{\rENG}We're going after Cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:15.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,叫他馬上降落 這是命令\N{\rENG}You tell him to land that plane That's an order
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:17.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,騎鬼者 你接到降落指示\N{\rENG}Ghost Rider, you are instructed to land,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬上降落\N{\rENG}Land immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們看到附近有航空母艦嗎\N{\rENG}Any of you boys seen an aircraft carrier around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:31.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們有點小問題 那架米格機嚇壞他了\N{\rENG}Mav, we got a little problem up here.That MiG really screwed him up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:33.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,他大概無法把戰機開回去\N{\rENG}I don't think he can make it back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:39.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅 不要緊 跟著我飛\N{\rENG}You're okay, Cougar Just stay on my wing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:43.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,我會帶你回去 跟著我\N{\rENG}I'll take you all the way in Just stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:02.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,別緊張 好像逛公園一樣\N{\rENG}Easy, Cougar Just a walk in the park, buddy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:06.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,你飛得低了點 低了一點\N{\rENG}You're a little low.You're a little low, Coug
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,老友 快點上升\N{\rENG}Come on, buddy, pull up
