Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:51.63,ZHU,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}美國空軍基地 加州米拉馬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,海軍在韓戰的殺敵比率 是十二比一\N{\rENG}During Korea, the Navy kill ratio was 12-to-1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:28.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們一架戰機 就能擊落敵人十二架\N{\rENG}We shot down 12 of their jets for every one of ours
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,到了越戰時比率降至三比一\N{\rENG}During Vietnam, that ratio fell to 3-to-1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們的機師太依賴導彈了\N{\rENG}Our pilots become dependent upon missiles
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:36.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們失去了一些空戰技巧\N{\rENG}They had lost some of their dogfighting skills
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:40.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,成立頂級機師部 是為了教導你們空戰策略\N{\rENG}Top Gun was created to teach ACM: Air Combat Maneuvering
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:42.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,也就是空中格鬥\N{\rENG}Dogfighting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:43.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,真令人興奮\N{\rENG}This gives me a hard-on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,到了越戰末期 比率回升至十二比一\N{\rENG}By the end of Vietnam, that ratio was back up to 12-to-1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:47.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,別跟我開玩笑\N{\rENG}Don't tease me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,請下窗簾\N{\rENG}Blinds, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:53.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想藉著這次機會 介紹指揮官給大家認識\N{\rENG}I'd like to take this opportunity to introduce you to our commanding officer at Top Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:56.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,他是第一位獲得 頂級機師獎的人\N{\rENG}The very first man to win the Top Gun trophy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不會在其他地方找到 比他更優秀的機師了\N{\rENG}You will not find a finer fighter pilot anywhere in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:02.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,麥米克長官 外號毒蛇\N{\rENG}Commander Mike Metcalf Callsign: Viper
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:04.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,各位\N{\rENG}Gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:10.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們是海軍空戰人員中 最好的百分之一\N{\rENG}You are the top one percent of all naval aviators
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:15.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,是精英 精英中之精英\N{\rENG}The elite The best of the best
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:18.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們會令你們更進一步\N{\rENG}We'll make you better
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:21.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們每天至少 要執行兩項空中任務\N{\rENG}You'll fly at least two combat missions a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:24.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,當中要上課 聽取自己表現所得到的評價\N{\rENG}attend classes in between and evaluations of your performance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:28.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們在每次的空中任務 都要面對新挑戰\N{\rENG}On each combat sequence, you're gonna meet a different challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:31.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,每一次都會更加困難\N{\rENG}Every encounter is gonna be much more difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們會教你們令F14盡展所長\N{\rENG}We're gonna teach you to fly the F-14 right to the edge of the envelope,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們會比以前開得更快\N{\rENG}faster than you've ever flown before
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:39.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,也會更加危險\N{\rENG}and more dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:42.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,各位 我們不是在這兒立法\N{\rENG}Now, we don't make policy here, gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:46.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,立法是由獲選的官員 和平民做的\N{\rENG}Elected officials, civilians do that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們只是這些政策的工具\N{\rENG}We are the instruments of that policy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:53.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,雖然我們不是在打仗 但要假裝是\N{\rENG}And although we're not at war,we must always act as though we are at war
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:54.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼\N{\rENG}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:59.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 矛尖最好鋒利點  - 我只是在想誰是最一流的機師\N{\rENG}- The tip of the spear best be sharp.  - I'm just wondering who's the best
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:02.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們可能會想 誰是最一流的機師\N{\rENG}In case some of you wonder who the best is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們的名字就在牆上的板子上\N{\rENG}they're up here on this plaque on the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:07.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,最佳機師和他的通訊員的名字 都會記錄在上面\N{\rENG}The best driver and his RIO from each class has his name on it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:13.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們可以選擇回來當教官\N{\rENG}And they have the option to come back here to be Top Gun instructors
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:19.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,你認為你的名字會在上面\N{\rENG}You think your name's gonna be on that plaque?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,是 長官\N{\rENG}Yes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:25.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,你真自大 周圍有這麼多人\N{\rENG}That's pretty arrogant, considering the company you're in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,是 長官\N{\rENG}Yes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:33.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,我喜歡機師自大\N{\rENG}I like that in a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:37.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,記著 離開這兒後 我們都是同一隊人\N{\rENG}Just remember, when it's over out there,we're all on the same team
