Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:50.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,做得好\N{\rENG}Nice going
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:57.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,後補者的徽章在女洗手間\N{\rENG}The plaque for the alternates is down in the ladies' room
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:03.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊 真是笑死我了\N{\rENG}Oh, Jesus Oh, you kill me You really do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:07.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 “野鵝” 是兩個O的\N{\rENG}No, no, no There's two O's in "Goose", boys
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:25.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,真是一個不愁沒目標的環境\N{\rENG}This is what I call a target-rich environment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:27.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在兩腿之間生活\N{\rENG}You live your life between your legs, Mav
