Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:34.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,能找到說髒話的女孩 我就高興了\N{\rENG}I'm telling you, I'd be happy to find a girl who'd talk dirty to me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:42.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力 你想知道誰是一流機師\N{\rENG}Mav, you wanted to know who the best is?
