Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:48.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,因為他開戰機時十分冷靜 從不犯錯\N{\rENG}That's the way he flies, ice-cold, no mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:53.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,磨滅你的耐性 令你沮喪 你一犯錯就會被他逮住\N{\rENG}Just wears you down.You get bored, frustrated, do something stupid, and he's got you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,滑行者\N{\rENG}Hey, hey, Slider
