Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:37.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,誰是最佳機師\N{\rENG}Who's the best pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,還沒有 我自己會想到的\N{\rENG}No, I think I can figure that one out on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:43.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,聽說你喜歡單獨行事\N{\rENG}I heard that about you You like to work alone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:48.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,你一定是在幸運星之下行事\N{\rENG}Mav, you must've soloed under a lucky star, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:51.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,先是米格機 然後又闖進美洲獅的戰場\N{\rENG}I mean, first the MiG,and then you guys slide into Cougar's spot
