Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:57.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,有些機師到退役時 還沒試過近距離見過米格機\N{\rENG}Some pilots wait their whole career just to see a MiG up close
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:59.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們一定是既幸運又出名了\N{\rENG}Guess you guys are lucky and famous, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:01.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想說的是臭名遠播吧\N{\rENG}No, you mean notorious
