Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:10.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道 從青春期開始\N{\rENG}Oh, I don't know, since-Puberty?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.84,0:23:12.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,對\N{\rENG}Right, puberty
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:15.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我叫布莎洛  - 我叫馬華力\N{\rENG}- I'm Charlotte Blackwood  - I'm Maverick
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.67,0:23:19.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力 你媽媽不喜歡你嗎\N{\rENG}Maverick? Did your mother not like you or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.51,0:23:21.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 這是我的外號\N{\rENG}No, it's my callsign
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.65,0:23:23.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是戰機師\N{\rENG}You're a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:25.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,是 我是海軍空戰人員\N{\rENG}That's right, a naval aviator
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.58,0:23:29.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,其實我們這樣做只試過兩次\N{\rENG}No, actually, we've only done this twice
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.39,0:23:31.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,結果怎樣\N{\rENG}Oh, how'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:34.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,第一次是一場大災難 不太好看\N{\rENG}Crashed and burned on the first one It wasn't pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.03,0:23:37.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,第二次呢\N{\rENG}The second?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.23,0:23:40.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道 明天告訴你 暫時還不錯\N{\rENG}I don't know I'll tell you tomorrow But it's looking good so far
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.64,0:23:45.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力\N{\rENG}Well, Maverick,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:48.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的朋友剛到了 和你談得真愉快\N{\rENG}my friend's just arrived, so it's been great talking to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:50.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 彼利  - 嗨\N{\rENG}- Perry  - Hi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.44,0:23:54.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,你來了 我馬上回來\N{\rENG}Hi Here you go I'll be with you in just a second, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:24:00.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以問你一個私人問題嗎\N{\rENG}Listen, can I ask you a personal question?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.49,0:24:02.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,視乎你問什麼\N{\rENG}That depends
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:06.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是好機師嗎\N{\rENG}Are you a good pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.29,0:24:09.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,我認為我是\N{\rENG}I can hold my own
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.33,0:24:16.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,好極 我不用擔心你要靠唱歌維生了\N{\rENG}Great Then I won't have to worry about you making your living as a singer
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.84,0:24:24.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我需要啤酒來救火\N{\rENG}I'm gonna need a beer to put these flames out Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.98,0:24:28.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,好極 真狡猾\N{\rENG}Great, Mav Real slick
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.87,0:24:54.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,水手 你出了海很久嗎\N{\rENG}It was a long cruise, was it, sailor?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.97,0:24:56.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,太久了\N{\rENG}It was too long
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.81,0:25:00.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想怎樣 就地進行嗎\N{\rENG}What did you wanna do,just drop right down on the tile and go for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.75,0:25:05.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 其實我是想在這張桌子\N{\rENG}No, I actually had...Had this counter in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.85,0:25:08.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,好極 一定會很舒服\N{\rENG}Great, that would be very, very comfortable Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.32,0:25:09.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能會\N{\rENG}It could be
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.76,0:25:19.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,其實我來是希望你不會 為那個老鬼做錯誤決定\N{\rENG}Actually,I came in here to save you from making a big mistake with that older guy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.53,0:25:25.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,真的 那我就能和你這種年輕人好\N{\rENG}Really?So I could go on to a bigger one with a young guy like yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.94,0:25:29.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能吧\N{\rENG}Maybe No?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.78,0:25:33.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,明天一早我便要工作\N{\rENG}I've gotta be at work very early in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.21,0:25:34.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在這兒做什麼\N{\rENG}Then what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.78,0:25:39.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的朋友真厲害\N{\rENG}Your friend was magnificent
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.76,0:25:45.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.39,0:25:51.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們也會受到 平民專家的訓練和評估\N{\rENG}Now, you'll also be trained and evaluated by a few civilian specialists
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.43,0:25:55.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,這兒有平民 是因為他們對敵機很有認識\N{\rENG}The civilians are here because they are our very best source of information on enemy aircraft
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.23,0:26:00.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,其中最有資格的 就是教官代表 外號狐狸\N{\rENG}One of the most qualified is our TAGREP,callsign: Charlie
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.20,0:26:02.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,她是天體物理學哲學博士\N{\rENG}She has a PhD in astrophysics,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.34,0:26:05.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,她也是一個平民承包商 你們不用向她敬禮\N{\rENG}and she's also a civilian contractor,so you do not salute her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.74,0:26:09.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,不過最好聽她的 因為軍方相信她對你們的評估\N{\rENG}But you better listen to her,because the Pentagon listens to her about your proficiency
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.78,0:26:11.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 交給你了 狐狸  - 謝謝\N{\rENG}- It's all yours, Charlie  - Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.45,0:26:14.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,大家好\N{\rENG}Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.55,0:26:19.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們會用F5和 A4模擬米格機\N{\rENG}We will be dealing with F-5s and A-4s as our MiG simulators
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.46,0:26:21.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們大多都應該知道\N{\rENG}Now, then, as most of you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.69,0:26:26.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,F5不像米格28 可以打破重量比率\N{\rENG}the F-5 doesn't have the thrust-to-weight ratio the MiG-28 has
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.50,0:26:30.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,更不會像米格28 在少於三百海海裡時漏出能量\N{\rENG}And it doesn't bleed energy below 300 knots, like the MiG-28
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.67,0:26:36.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,不過米格28的反飛行油箱 的確有問題\N{\rENG}However, the MiG-28 does have a problem with its inverted flight tanks
