Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.81,0:26:42.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,最新的情報告訴我們\N{\rENG}The latest intelligence tells us that the most it will do
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.25,0:26:44.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,它最多能夠做負一\N{\rENG}is one negative...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.95,0:26:47.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,對不起 上尉\N{\rENG}Excuse me, lieutenant
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.35,0:26:49.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎\N{\rENG}Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.85,0:26:52.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,是 米格機的資料不正確\N{\rENG}Yes, ma'am, the data on the MiG is inaccurate
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.96,0:26:55.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,哪兒不正確\N{\rENG}How's that, lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.19,0:26:59.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我看過米格28…  - 是我們\N{\rENG}- Well, I just happened to see a MiG-28 do...  - We, we
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.63,0:27:00.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,對不起 野鵝\N{\rENG}Sorry, Goose
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.97,0:27:04.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們見過米格28 做四個負引力俯衝\N{\rENG}We happened to see a MiG-28 do a four-G negative dive
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.27,0:27:08.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在哪兒見到\N{\rENG}Where did you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.21,0:27:10.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是機密資料\N{\rENG}That's classified
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.41,0:27:12.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\rENG}It's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.34,0:27:13.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,是機密資料\N{\rENG}It's classified
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.28,0:27:15.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以告訴你 但是之後就要殺了你\N{\rENG}I could tell you, but I'd have to kill you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.05,0:27:18.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,上尉 我有權知道最高機密\N{\rENG}Lieutenant, I have top-secret clearance
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.08,0:27:22.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,軍方要我比你知道得更多\N{\rENG}The Pentagon sees to it that I know more than you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.86,0:27:26.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,那麼這次大概不同了\N{\rENG}Well, ma'am, it doesn't seem so in this case, now, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.49,0:27:31.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,上尉 你當時在哪兒\N{\rENG}So, lieutenant where exactly were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.93,0:27:34.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我們  - 謝謝\N{\rENG}- Well, we.  - Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.10,0:27:39.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們從他後面開始 他穿越雲層 我飛到他上面\N{\rENG}started up on his 6 when he pulled through the clouds,and then I moved in above him
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.17,0:27:42.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在他上面又怎會看到他\N{\rENG}Well, if you were directly above him, how could you see him?
