Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.94,0:27:46.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,廢話\N{\rENG}Bullshit
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.25,0:27:48.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 他真是這樣做\N{\rENG}No, he was, man It was a really great move
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.21,0:27:51.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,好精彩呢 他倒轉了\N{\rENG}He was inverted
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.22,0:27:56.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,你和米格28一起 做四個負引力反轉俯衝\N{\rENG}You were in a four-G inverted dive with a MiG-28?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.79,0:27:58.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rENG}Yes, ma'am
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.36,0:28:01.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 距離多遠  - 大概兩米吧\N{\rENG}- At what range?  - About two meters
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.93,0:28:04.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,實際上是一米半\N{\rENG}It was actually about one and a half, I think
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.56,0:28:05.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,我拍下了當時的精彩景象\N{\rENG}It was one and a half.I've got a great Polaroid of it
