Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.94,0:28:16.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 溝通  - 溝通\N{\rENG}- Communicating  - Communicating
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.21,0:28:19.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,是溝通 保持外交關係\N{\rENG}Keeping up foreign relations
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.78,0:28:22.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,我當時在向他喝倒彩\N{\rENG}I was You know, giving him the bird
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.28,0:28:24.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,用手指表示\N{\rENG}You know, the finger
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.08,0:28:27.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我明白 野鵝\N{\rENG}Yes, I know the finger, Goose
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.32,0:28:29.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,對不起 我討厭它這樣\N{\rENG}I'm sorry, I hate it when it does that I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.99,0:28:32.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\rENG}Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.22,0:28:34.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,原來是你\N{\rENG}So you're the one
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.49,0:28:36.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rENG}Yes, ma'am
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.00,0:28:40.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 各位 我們要飛行了\N{\rENG}All right, gentlemen, we have a hop to take
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.87,0:28:44.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,假設地面在一萬英尺 無論如何不能低過這高度\N{\rENG}The hard deck on this hop will be 10000 feet.There'll be no engagement below that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.44,0:28:46.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,出發\N{\rENG}Move it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.84,0:28:53.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,上尉\N{\rENG}Lieutenant
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.85,0:28:57.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,別再遲到 親愛的\N{\rENG}Okay, well, don't be late again.You look great, honey
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.82,0:29:00.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝 在預飛區見\N{\rENG}Thanks, dear See you in preflight
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.28,0:29:04.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,上尉 你為什麼不告訴我 是你羞辱米格機\N{\rENG}Lieutenant,why didn't you tell me that you were the famous MiG insulter?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.82,0:29:06.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,我說了會有分別嗎\N{\rENG}Would it have made any difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.49,0:29:08.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,在女洗手間裡不會\N{\rENG}Not in the ladies' room, no
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.69,0:29:09.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我們呢\N{\rENG}What would've?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.36,0:29:12.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是這兒的教官\N{\rENG}I'm an instructor at this school
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.26,0:29:14.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,每八個星期就會見到 二十個雄心勃勃的新丁\N{\rENG}I see 20 new hotshots every eight weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.80,0:29:17.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,你一定能想像得到\N{\rENG}Now, I'm sure you can figure that out
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.44,0:29:18.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,上尉\N{\rENG}Look, lieutenant
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.87,0:29:22.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真的很想聽聽米格機的事\N{\rENG}I'd just really like to hear about the MiG sometime
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.91,0:29:28.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,你有權看最高機密 你可以自己看\N{\rENG}You've got security clearance.You can read about it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.95,0:29:35.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力\N{\rENG}Maverick
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.22,0:29:38.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很好奇\N{\rENG}I'm curious
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.52,0:29:45.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,你戲弄米格機時 是誰在掩護美洲獅\N{\rENG}Who was covering Cougar while you were showboating with this MiG?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.16,0:29:48.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,美洲獅表現很好\N{\rENG}Cougar was doing just fine
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.10,0:29:51.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,先生們 這是你們的第一跳\N{\rENG}Gentlemen, this is your first hop,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.14,0:29:55.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們面對的戰機更小 更快 也更容易控制\N{\rENG}The jets you are flying against are smaller, faster and more maneuverable,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.77,0:29:57.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像米格機一樣\N{\rENG}just like the enemy MiGs,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.41,0:30:00.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,計時開始 我們要保持優勢\N{\rENG}The clock is ticking and as of now,we are keeping score,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.35,0:30:02.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不見了他 野鵝\N{\rENG}I lost him, Goose
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.58,0:30:06.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,小子 讓我看看你有什麼能耐\N{\rENG}Show me what you got, kid
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.15,0:30:07.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,不見了他\N{\rENG}I lost him
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.05,0:30:09.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我在找他了\N{\rENG}I'm looking, I'm looking
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.09,0:30:14.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,看到了 他在我們後面沖過來\N{\rENG}I got him, I got him.He's on our tail, coming hard
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.23,0:30:16.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,我看到他了 行動\N{\rENG}I got him I got him Here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.54,0:30:30.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 把資料告訴我 野鵝\N{\rENG}All right, talk to me, Goose
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.74,0:30:34.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,他仍然在很後面 急速飛過來\N{\rENG}He's still back there He's closing in on us.He's closing fast
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.48,0:30:36.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,小子 你可以逃 但是躲不掉\N{\rENG}You can run, kid, but you can't hide
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.85,0:30:43.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,笑匠 看看我能不能逼你盡力\N{\rENG}Come on, Jester.Let's see if I can give you a run for your money here
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.06,0:30:51.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,小心撞山\N{\rENG}Watch the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.04,0:31:03.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,我仍然看到他 他仍然在後面\N{\rENG}I still got him He's still back there
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.14,0:31:06.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力 快點想辦法\N{\rENG}Come on, Mav Do some of that pilot shit
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.31,0:31:07.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,我看到他了\N{\rENG}Yeah, I got him
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.86,0:31:19.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,快點鎖定\N{\rENG}Come on, bring it right
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.63,0:31:22.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,野鵝 我受夠了\N{\rENG}Goose, I've had about enough of this shit
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.46,0:31:26.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要踏制動器 他就會飛過頭\N{\rENG}I'm gonna hit the brakes, he'll fly right by
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.50,0:31:27.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們死定了\N{\rENG}Okay, you're mine
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.27,0:31:37.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\rENG}Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.01,0:31:42.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,看看你現在的境況 笑匠\N{\rENG}Let's see what you've got now, Jester
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.01,0:31:45.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,扭轉局勢吧\N{\rENG}Okay, Mav, let's turn and burn
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.17,0:32:04.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,他垂直飛 我也是\N{\rENG}He's going vertical, so am I
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.97,0:32:07.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們好像在彈射一樣\N{\rENG}We're going ballistic, Mav Go get him
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.75,0:32:19.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,他要飛向假設地面 快比他搶先一步\N{\rENG}He's going for the hard deck.Let's get down there first and nail him, Mav
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.08,0:32:22.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,不行 笑匠 你死定了\N{\rENG}No way, Jester, you're mine
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.04,0:32:40.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,我瞄準你了\N{\rENG}I got you now
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.61,0:32:45.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,笑匠輸了\N{\rENG}Jester's dead
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.88,0:32:47.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,笑匠輸了\N{\rENG}Jester's dead
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.55,0:32:53.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬上飛高回基地\N{\rENG}Get your butts above the hard deck and return to base immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.66,0:32:58.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,遵命\N{\rENG}Yes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.13,0:33:08.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,控制塔 騎鬼者要求低飛\N{\rENG}Tower, this is Ghost Rider requesting a flyby
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.20,0:33:11.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,騎鬼者 不行 航線繁忙\N{\rENG}Negative, Ghost Rider, the pattern is full
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.80,0:33:14.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 馬華力 這不是個好主意\N{\rENG}No No, Mav This is not a good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.27,0:33:17.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,對不起 野鵝 是時候飛過控制塔了\N{\rENG}Sorry, Goose, but it's time to buzz the tower
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.85,0:33:31.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,臭小子\N{\rENG}Goddamn son of a bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.09,0:33:37.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,真是精彩絕倫\N{\rENG}Great balls of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.20,0:33:42.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,笑匠輸了\N{\rENG}Jester's dead
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.17,0:33:44.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們贏了 廢話\N{\rENG}You won? That's bullshit
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.20,0:33:45.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是大家都贏了嗎\N{\rENG}Didn't everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.24,0:33:47.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,是才怪 我們都慘敗而回\N{\rENG}Hell, no, man, we got our butts kicked
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.47,0:33:50.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,在三十秒內我們這樣 他這樣\N{\rENG}Thirty seconds We went like this, he went like that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.37,0:33:55.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我問好萊塢他在哪兒 他竟然問我誰在哪兒\N{\rENG}I said to Hollywood, "Where'd he go?"Hollywood said, "Where'd who go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.41,0:33:58.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,他就在對講機上取笑我們\N{\rENG}Yeah, and he's laughing at us,right on the radio He's laughing at us
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.18,0:33:59.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 笑你們的是我 笨蛋\N{\rENG}No, it's me laughing, dickhead
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.92,0:34:00.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們贏了\N{\rENG}We won
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.05,0:34:03.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rENG}All right
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.22,0:34:04.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們也贏了呢\N{\rENG}They won too, man
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.56,0:34:07.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我沒聽說過  - 是真的 我們打敗了笑匠\N{\rENG}- That's not what I heard  - No, we did, we got Jester
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.79,0:34:10.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 低過假設地面不算\N{\rENG}No, no Below the hard deck does not count
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.80,0:34:13.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,假設地面 總之我們打敗了他\N{\rENG}Hard deck, my ass.We nailed that son of a bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.86,0:34:15.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們真愛自吹自擂\N{\rENG}You guys really are cowboys
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.27,0:34:17.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,卡湯姆 你有問題嗎\N{\rENG}What's your problem, Kazansky?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.00,0:34:20.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是大家的問題\N{\rENG}You're everyone's problem
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.97,0:34:23.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,因為你每次飛行都不安全\N{\rENG}That's because every time you go up in the air,you're unsafe
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.87,0:34:25.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不喜歡你 因為你很危險\N{\rENG}I don't like you because you're dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.71,0:34:29.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,對 冰佬\N{\rENG}That's right, Iceman
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.11,0:34:32.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很危險\N{\rENG}I am dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.72,0:34:36.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力\N{\rENG}Maverick, you and Goose get your butts out of that flight gear
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.42,0:34:40.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,你和野鵝馬上脫掉飛行衣 到毒蛇的辦公室\N{\rENG}and up to Viper's office now
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.56,0:34:47.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,記著 當第二名是沒分的\N{\rENG}Remember, boys, no points for second place
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.10,0:34:50.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你們比看來更聰明  - 住口\N{\rENG}- You're a lot brighter than you look  - You shut up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.10,0:34:52.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 別擔心 野鵝  - 我會\N{\rENG}- Don't worry, Goose, don't worry  - Okay, I will
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.87,0:34:57.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,有這兩個自大狂 以四百多海海裡飛過控制塔\N{\rENG}Two of your snot-nosed jockeys did a flyby on my tower at over 400 knots!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.24,0:35:00.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要你們找人負責 我受夠了\N{\rENG}I want somebody's butt I want it now I've had it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.61,0:35:04.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,該死 第二次了\N{\rENG}Goddamn it! That's twice
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.02,0:35:06.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,一定要有人負責\N{\rENG}I want some butts!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.05,0:35:10.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,正好解釋了飛過控制塔的事\N{\rENG}Well, that'll just about cover the flybys
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.12,0:35:13.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,跟我來\N{\rENG}Follow me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.70,0:35:23.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,兩位 你們第一天過得真充實\N{\rENG}Gentlemen You had a hell of a first day
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.70,0:35:29.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,這次任務的假設地面是一萬英尺\N{\rENG}The hard deck for this hop was 10000 feet
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.07,0:35:31.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們明知故犯\N{\rENG}You knew it, you broke it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.11,0:35:37.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,希軍官不見了你們之後 你們跟著他低飛\N{\rENG}You followed Commander Heatherly below after he lost sight of you and called no joy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.68,0:35:39.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,為什麼\N{\rENG}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.15,0:35:44.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,長官 我看到希軍官\N{\rENG}Sir I had Commander Heatherly in my sights.He saw me move in for the kill
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.26,0:35:49.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,他看到我飛到開火的位置 就飛低過假設地面\N{\rENG}He then proceeded below the hard deck
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.96,0:35:53.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們只有幾秒低飛了\N{\rENG}We weren't below 10000 for more than a few seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.56,0:35:57.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我瞄準了他 見沒有危險就開火\N{\rENG}I had the shot, there was no danger, so I took it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.97,0:36:03.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,你開了火 你破壞了重要守則\N{\rENG}You took it And broke a major rule of engagement
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.97,0:36:08.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,飛越控制塔時又犯了另一條\N{\rENG}Then you broke another one with that circus-stunt flyby
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.28,0:36:11.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,麥上尉\N{\rENG}Lieutenant Mitchell, Top Gun rules of engagement exist
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.65,0:36:15.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,守則是為了你 和隊員的安全而設立的\N{\rENG}for your safety and for that of your team
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.75,0:36:18.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,守則不可隨時更改 我也是\N{\rENG}They are not flexible, nor am I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.02,0:36:22.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,不遵守的話就要被開除 清楚了嗎\N{\rENG}Either obey them or you're history.Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.16,0:36:25.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,是 長官\N{\rENG}Yes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.14,0:36:35.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,解散\N{\rENG}Dismissed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.18,0:36:43.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真的很享受那一下 謝謝你\N{\rENG}I really enjoyed that, Mav, thanks a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.68,0:36:45.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\rENG}Holy shit
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.69,0:36:51.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我或者可以學習當貨車司機\N{\rENG}Maybe I could learn how to be a truck driver
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.02,0:36:55.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,你有貨車駕駛學校的電話號碼\N{\rENG}Mav, you have the number of that truck-driving school we saw on TV?Truck Master, I think it is
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.99,0:36:57.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可能會需要到\N{\rENG}I might need that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.60,0:37:02.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,評估報告已經顯示了他很飄忽\N{\rENG}His fitness report says it all.He's a wild card
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.47,0:37:05.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,他靠直覺開戰機 完全無法預測\N{\rENG}Flies by the seat of his pants.Completely unpredictable
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.57,0:37:10.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 他嚇倒你了  - 是\N{\rENG}- He got you, didn't he?  - Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.11,0:37:16.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力 我曾經和他爸爸共事\N{\rENG}Maverick I flew with his old man
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.85,0:37:24.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,告訴我 你想和他一起上戰場嗎\N{\rENG}Tell me one thing.If you had to go into battle, would you want him with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.42,0:37:26.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.39,0:37:28.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真的不知道\N{\rENG}I just don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.77,0:37:42.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,還沒睡嗎\N{\rENG}You still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.74,0:37:44.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rENG}Yeah
