Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.93,0:51:31.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在米格機的射程範圍 你現在會想什麼\N{\rENG}The MiG has you in his gunsight What were you thinking at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.24,0:51:34.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,你沒時間在空中思想了\N{\rENG}You don't have time to think up there
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.30,0:51:37.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,一想就死定了\N{\rENG}If you think, you're dead
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.34,0:51:40.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,用價值三千萬元的戰機打賭 賭得可真大呢\N{\rENG}Well, that's a big gamble with a $30 million plane, lieutenant
