Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.22,0:51:52.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,米格機無法開火\N{\rENG}The MiG never got a clean shot
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.32,0:51:56.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力做了 富侵略性的垂直飛行\N{\rENG}Maverick makes an aggressive vertical move here,
