Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.36,0:52:02.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,這次的交手是一次勝利\N{\rENG}The encounter was a victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.23,0:52:06.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,不過這是不該做的例子\N{\rENG}but I think that we've shown it as an example of what not to do
