Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.04,0:52:12.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,從沒見過這麼大膽的行動\N{\rENG}Gutsiest move I ever saw, man
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.21,0:52:20.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,接著的可以作為 教科書的最佳例子\N{\rENG}Now, then, this is a perfect example of a textbook maneuver
