Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.20,0:52:40.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬華力\N{\rENG}Maverick
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.34,0:52:47.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,上尉\N{\rENG}Lieutenant Lieutenant
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.24,0:52:53.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,我對你的飛行評估 是我的專業意見\N{\rENG}My review of your flight performance in the TACTS was right on, in my professional opinion
