Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.75,0:53:27.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我對你的飛行評估是正確的\N{\rENG}My review of your flight performance was right on
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.45,0:53:29.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是嗎？  - 是的\N{\rENG}- Is that right?  - That is right
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.32,0:53:31.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是我保留了一些\N{\rENG}But I held something back
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.15,0:53:34.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,我看得出你有飛行的天才 但是我不能在那兒說出來\N{\rENG}I see some real genius in your flying,Maverick, but I can't say that in there
