Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.65,0:55:43.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,我感覺到我需要速度\N{\rENG}I feel the need, the need for speed! The need for speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.42,0:55:48.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,各位 這是第十九次飛行\N{\rENG}Gentlemen, this is hop 19,
