Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.55,0:57:26.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,好萊塢 你進展良好\N{\rENG}Hollywood, you're looking good
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.86,0:57:28.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,我去對付毒蛇\N{\rENG}I'm going after Viper
