Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.50,0:58:44.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,繼續\N{\rENG}Come on, come on, come on, keep coming Keep coming
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.57,0:58:49.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,加油\N{\rENG}Come on, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.41,0:58:56.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,該死 這小子真厲害\N{\rENG}Damn, this kid's good
