Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.15,1:00:13.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是你比敵人更加危險\N{\rENG}but right now you're worse than the enemy
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.06,1:00:16.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,你既危險又愚蠢\N{\rENG}You're dangerous and foolish
