Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.02,1:20:17.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\rENG}Look, thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.86,1:20:22.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想別人幫我的話 自然會開口\N{\rENG}But if I wanted help, really,I would have asked for it
