Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.50,1:21:34.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 珍美 你要喝點什麼嗎  - 不必了\N{\rENG}- Jamie, come on.Can I get you a drink or anything else like that?  - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.26,1:21:38.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,請隨便坐 米克馬上就下來了\N{\rENG}Okay, well, why don't you just make yourself comfortable Mike will be right down
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.97,1:21:40.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\rENG}Great, thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.39,1:22:03.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,你爸爸和我在奧利士卡尼號的VF51小隊並肩作戰\N{\rENG}I flew with your old man VF-51, the Oriskany
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.77,1:22:13.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,你真的很像他\N{\rENG}You're a lot like he was Only better and worse
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.04,1:22:18.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,他是一個天生的英雄主義者\N{\rENG}He was a natural heroic son of a bitch, that one
