Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.99,1:22:31.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 他沒做錯\N{\rENG}Yeah, he did it right
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.17,1:22:45.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以你這樣開戰機 你想證明什麼\N{\rENG}Is that why you fly the way you do?Trying to prove something?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.51,1:22:49.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,你爸爸的確沒做錯\N{\rENG}Yeah, your old man did it right
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.58,1:22:55.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要告訴你的事是機密事件 可能會令我丟掉工作\N{\rENG}What I'm about to tell you is classified.It could end my career
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.52,1:22:58.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們置身於一場 我夢寐以求的戰鬥之中\N{\rENG}We were in the worst dogfight I ever dreamed of
