Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.76,1:23:06.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,他的F4戰機被擊中 他受了傷\N{\rENG}His F-4 was hit, he was wounded,but he could've made it back
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.36,1:23:08.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,他本來可以回基地 但是他留在戰場\N{\rENG}He stayed in it, saved three planes
