Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.37,1:23:49.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,這不是丟臉的事 那樣打轉我也會被嚇倒\N{\rENG}There'd be no disgrace That spin was hell.It would've shook me up
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.37,1:23:51.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,你認為我應該退學\N{\rENG}So you think I should quit?
