Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.19,1:24:17.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,到了高空我們就要全力以赴 這是我們的職責\N{\rENG}Up there, we gotta push it That's our job
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.44,1:24:24.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,上尉 這全看你的選擇\N{\rENG}It's your option, lieutenant, all yours
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.18,1:24:38.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,對不起 在周日打擾你\N{\rENG}Sorry to bother you on a Sunday, sir,
